OL,3,CSex offender jailed for rapes against
OL,4,Cwoman and historic abuse of children
OL,6,FA man from Birmingham has been jailed
OL,7,Ffor 21 years for rapes against a
OL,8,Fwoman, and historic rape and sexual
OL,9,Fabuse of two children.
OL,11,FWest Midlands Police say Marcus
OL,12,FNewton's crimes came to light after
OL,13,Fhis three brave victims came forward.
OL,15,FNewton who is 27 and from Aston, was
OL,16,Fjailed after a trial at Wolverhampton
OL,17,FCrown Court on 26th July.
OL,19,FHe was also placed on the Sex
OL,20,FOffenders Register for life.
