OL,6,FHe was found guilty of two charges of
OL,7,Fraping a child under 13, one charge of
OL,8,Fsexually assaulting a child under 13,
OL,9,Fand three charges of rape.
OL,11,FOfficers say they were made aware of
OL,12,Fhis offences after one of his victims
OL,13,Fcontacted them to say that he had been
OL,14,Fraped by Newton.
OL,16,FHe told police how Newton's actions
OL,17,Fhad a massive impact on his mental
OL,18,Fhealth, and that the offending took
OL,19,Fplace when he was a young boy.
