OL,6,FTwo more victims then came forward -
OL,7,Fone was a woman who said she had been
OL,8,Fraped by Newton in 2018 and 2019.
OL,10,FAnother woman then came forward to say
OL,11,Fshe had been raped by Newton over a
OL,12,Fperiod of four years, while she was
OL,13,Fstill a child.
OL,15,FPolice say they analysed footage on
OL,16,Fher phone, which included messages and
OL,17,Fpictures sent by Newton to corroborate
OL,18,Fher story.
OL,20,F"Newton has shown no signs of remorse"
