OL,6,FDetective Sergeant Sareena Puri from
OL,7,Fthe Adult Investigation Team said:
OL,9,F"Newton is a sexual predator who raped
OL,10,Fand sexually abused his vulnerable
OL,11,Fvictims.
OL,13,F"Two of them were under the age of 13
OL,14,Fat the time.
OL,16,F"We are pleased with the sentence
OL,17,Fwhich sends out a clear message that
OL,18,Fpeople who behave in this appalling
OL,19,Fway will be caught and will spend many
OL,20,Fyears behind bars.
