OL,6,F"I would like to praise the courage of
OL,7,Fhis three victims who came forward to
OL,8,Ftell us what he had done.
OL,10,F"Their bravery in giving evidence in
OL,11,Fcourt has to be commended.
OL,13,FNewton has shown no signs of remorse
OL,14,Ffor what he has done and for the
OL,15,Fimpact his offending has had on the
OL,16,Flives of his three victims.
OL,18,F"We hope their bravery encourages
OL,19,Fother people subjected to sexual abuse
OL,20,Fand rape to come forward. We are here
OL,21,Fto help and listen."
